parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and deterioration of the dashboard can cause a distraction to the driver, potentially leading to accidents, and may also compromise the airbag system, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The dashboard is cracked
sticky
or glazed
obstructing vision due to sun reflection
and in some cases
the dashboard is peeling off or crumbling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and uncontrollably
even when the brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel well can cause the spare tire to fall to the ground, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: A noise comes from the wheel winch that holds the spare tire
and the wheel well breaks
causing the tire to fall to the ground.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window molding can cause a distraction to the driver and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The window molding comes flying off while driving
making a flapping noise beforehand.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Steering Rack and Pinion Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering rack and pinion can cause difficulty steering, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Leaking power steering fluid
difficulty steering
whining or buzzing noise when turning the steering wheel
steering wheel vibration or shaking
loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause loss of control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Steering wheel makes a whining or buzzing noise
difficulty steering
steering wheel vibration or shaking
loss of power steering assist
steering wheel locks or becomes stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Melting Dashboard and Steering Mechanism Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting of the dashboard can cause damage to the steering mechanism, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Melting dashboard
cracks in the dashboard
difficulty steering
steering wheel vibration or shaking
loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. Sudden acceleration can also lead to accidents, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
often without the driver pressing the accelerator pedal. The vehicle may lunge forward
surge
or take off rapidly
making it difficult for the driver to control. In some cases
the vehicle may accelerate when the cruise control is engaged
especially when driving uphill or on inclines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning cruise control system can cause unintended acceleration, leading to loss of vehicle control and accidents.
symptoms: The cruise control system fails to maintain the set speed
causing the vehicle to accelerate or decelerate unexpectedly. The vehicle may surge or lunge forward when the cruise control is engaged
especially when driving uphill or on inclines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Vehicle hesitation and stuttering can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stutters when accelerating
making it difficult for the driver to maintain control. The vehicle may stumble or jerk forward
causing the driver to lose confidence in the vehicle's performance.
